Document: cdk-pixdata
Title: CdkPixdata-2.0 Reference Manual
Author: CTK Development Team
Abstract: CdkPixdata is a deprecated pixel buffer format used to embed
 uncompressed images into libraries and executables.
 New code should use GResource to embed images in their compressed form
 instead.
Section: Programming/C

Format: HTML
Index: /usr/share/doc/libcdk-pixbuf2.0-doc/html/cdk-pixdata/index.html
Files: /usr/share/doc/libcdk-pixbuf2.0-doc/html/cdk-pixdata/*.html
